{"skipTransitionList":[],"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_01","textHome":"美术品真是漂亮啊。我正在水名美术馆打工。@因为我的梦想是成为美术品修复师，@所以就打算从接近美术品开始。@虽然也有过挫折，但大家却都温柔地带着我，@所以我会一直努力！下次，记得来我这玩哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_18","textHome":"父亲他，生前也是从事美术方面的工作的。@所以，我也想从事这方面的工作。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_19","textHome":"我变强了！我变强了对吧……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":303200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_20","textHome":"我感觉力量涌了出来……我会更加努力的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_21","textHome":"我在成为魔法少女之前，从来没有拿过武器，@也没有和人吵过架。@所以，我稍微有些害怕战斗。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":303200,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_22","textHome":"不管和魔女还有使魔战斗了多少次，@我都没办法习惯……一直都是畏手畏脚的……@因为感觉很害怕。@不过，这城市……神滨……水名……@都是我最喜欢的地方。@所以我必须要守护这里。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":303200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_00_23","textHome":"我想过了，为什么我会这么喜欢这城市呢……@因为这城市历史悠久，虽然并没有在文献中@留存下来，但是在这里生活的人们都和我息@息相关。我喜欢这样的城市……所以我也想@伴随着这城市。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":303200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":303200,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303250,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3032_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":303250,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":303250,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":